FuncDef: The pki delete-file command deletes a certificate file saved on the Flash. The pki delete-file command deletes a certificate file saved on the Flash.

ParaDef.Info:
Specifies the name of the certificate file to be deleted.
The value is a string of 1 to 64  case-sensitive characters, and cannot contain spaces.

Examples: Warning: Confirm to delete the file?Please select [Y/N]:y
